name: Baked Chicken With Puttanesca Sauce Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 180Â°C. Heat oil in an ovenproof pan over medium heat. Cook onion and garlic for 5 minutes or until tender. Stir in tomatoes, chilli flakes, olives and capers and bring mixture to the boil. Add chicken to pan, covering with sauce.
Transfer to oven and bake for 20 minutes or until chicken is cooked through. Sprinkle with parsley and serve with salad.
